      "_variants_note": "STT-calibrated: 'та едно' is how faster-whisper renders the A1 brand 'Моят А1' -> '...Та Едно'. NOTE: two common tokens — small false-pass risk on this HARD check; the more-specific 'моя та едно' was tried but STT renders 'моя' inconsistently and it false-NEGATIVES, so 'та едно' is the robust choice. Re-tune as more labelled calls arrive.",
