      "primitive": "phrase_present",
      "tier": "soft",
      "_note": "Surfaces the client-watched «не искат решение» (FirstWorkflow.md:17). Phrases seeded from the contract's ask_for_decision_phrases + CallScript closing asks. Excludes courier-address prompts like «на кой адрес» (that is address capture, not a decision ask — would false-pass). CALIBRATION-PENDING — tune on labelled calls.",
      "phrases": [
        "да запишем",
        "да продължим",
        "съгласни ли сте",
        "потвърждавате",
        "да активираме",
