      "id": "praise_benefits",
      "primitive": "phrase_present",
      "tier": "soft",
      "_note": "Surfaces «не хвалят / не дават практически ползи» (FirstWorkflow.md:17). Phrases seeded from the CallScript benefit language. Excludes near-universal words like «безплатно»/«на разположение» (appear on nearly every call → false-pass). CALIBRATION-PENDING — tune on labelled calls.",
      "phrases": [
