  "_stt_prompt_note": "A1-specific brand/product PROSE appended to the language pack's generic telco prose and fed to faster-whisper initial_prompt, to bias transcription. MUST be a natural sentence, NOT a keyword list (a bare list makes Whisper echo the names back — verified). This is the CORRECT boundary for the identify_a1 fidelity gap (fix the transcript, not add garbled aliases to the rubric). Note: the spoken brand 'Моят А1' (= 'Моят А-едно') still garbles at the very call opening on 8kHz even with priming; priming most helps the device/package/domain terms. Re-tune as more labelled calls arrive.",
